<h1>Mac Repair in {{ suburb.name }}</h1>

{# Section 2: Localised Intro Paragraph - location mentioned once here only #}
<section class="intro-section">
<p class="intro">If your MacBook or iMac has stopped working properly and you live in {{ suburb.name }}, our independent repair workshop can help. We fix issues like batteries that no longer hold a charge, cracked or flickering screens, keyboards with unresponsive keys, and Macs that won't turn on at all. Every repair starts with a hands-on diagnostic so you understand exactly what went wrong and what it costs to fix before we begin any work.</p>

<p>Our technician works at component level on logic boards, replaces genuine-spec batteries, recovers data from failing drives, and upgrades older Macs with solid state storage. Whether you use your Mac for work, university, or managing daily life, we aim to return it in reliable working condition with a clear explanation of what was done and why.</p>
</section>

